144 weeks ago I last was on live journal and updated. April 10th, 2006. Nearly 3 years ago. Wow. Time has gone so fast.

I remember when LJ was popular. It's now been shunned by myspace, facebook, and blogspot. It's a sad, sad world. Whatever happen to the good ole days? Seriously.

Time goes too fast. I mean, I was 17 years old when I last posted. I am now nearly 21. It's crazy crazy crazy.

I think we should bring back the LJ!!!!!

I waste my time...

no one will ever read this :(


Ps: I seen Gran Turismo tonight. amazing movie. I love.love.love Clint Eastwood, he is an amazing actor. Being so far in age, he still nails his roles. Go see it if you haven't already, Its a 5 star movie to me anyway,.

hey peoples, waz goin on? nm hurr..last night and today i house sat with cody and john at johns aunts house..last night, i met with john at hollywood video..we got splinter cell pandora tomorrow(not that good, wasnt 2 player like we thought..) some game i 4got the name but sucked really bad lol..and then Conflict Desert Storm 2 or suttin like that..now thats a great game..we played co op and owned all :P not really but we did beat quite a few missions in so many house straight playin..and today, did same thing..except, us 3 went mowing..mowed 3 yards, made an easy $18 or so each in less than 2 hours countin drivin n stuff..then we came back, more video games..and john left and me n cody played games for awhile..then i left and here i amm lol..so thats it for now..good bye

hey guys..lets see, yesterday was wednesday..school itself was boring and easy like always..played a little basketball..spanish 2 was easy, just hadda write down notes for a test tomorrow..then after that, i got changed, and walked down to the park..and of course i did the usual, of writing..but, while i was sittin there at picnic bench, outta no where these 2 girls come up to me and start talking..im thinkin, must be the hair cut :P j/p..it was weird, so they left after asking if i wanted to be left alone like a minute or two later..so i was glad of that...so then i wrote more, and walked back to uth..it was really really good..i think it's one of the best ever..i hope we have it like that in the future again..then today, same as yesterday, just today, football was added in the picture..great times like always..back in 9th grade(2 years ago), playin basketball, i hurt my shoulder some how..but i thought it was fine cause it eventually got better..but now like the last week or two, it's been aggravting me a lot and hurting..my mom thinks i could end up with surgery on somethin in it, i forget what she said it could be lol..so if that happens, don't let it be a surprise lol, but i doubt it will..i'll be fineeee..then was spanish, which we just were studying for tomorrows test, so i just slept lol..then i went to 7 11 and gots a drink and then headed home and here i am lol..this weekend i go house sitting with 2 of my homies, davis and cody..great times prolly.

today..was another good day..besides school being so boring like always lol..spanish, the teach. wasn't here, soo it made our 3rd straight day w/o spanish...soo i was able to come home today nice and early :) i played some socom from about 1:15-3:00..then went and got my hair cut..finally..then came home, just got on aim and listen to sum tunes which is what im still doing..tomorrow is uth day, soo i get to walk to el park-o after school and write again :)..welp, thats all for now..peace my homies!

welp, today was a great day..just kinda chilled and relaxed..didnt do anything lol, just listened to music and talked on aim..welp, this will be a short post cause i dont know what to say..peace my homies

today was a really good day..some past memories were brought up, like last summer when me,cody,lailhene,nikki, and cat went to busch gardens, man, that day was awesome, somethings i'm never gonna forget hehe so funny..anyways, there was a lot of laughter..and once again, me,cody and justin cleaned the tables n stuff after lunches..but today, we made a deal where we got to leave to get lunch, went to quiznos, omg soo good, i never had them b4, it's yummy..anyways, i totally forgot what a good driver wagner was lol,i've missed it..i also miss the "dr",man, it's been months :( oh well..anyways, then i hadda go to spanish, had a quiz i totally forgot to study for, but it was easy so i got a 90% woo hoo...also played basketball, tipped JJ out(haha yeah :P) and won the only game i played..that's pretty much how my really good day went..tomorrow is friday :) and the weekenddd..but then i think about how boring it's gonna be lol..i suppose that's all i gots ta say fo now..later days dudes and dudettes

well,today at school, it was boring.me,cody,and wagner cleaned the lunch room after eac lunch..we get 2 pizzas and each a drink on friday, so thats why lol, no way we'd do it for nuttin :P...anyways, that was easy, but very boring.then i went outside, and played basketball, good times like always..coach tippin me, me tippin him lol..well,then was spanish, easy like always too..then after school i walked to 7-11 to get some stuff and then went to the park, that's actually helping me a lot lol, like takes all my stress away for a bit..well, also, there was these 2 guys and a girl, they walked up to one of the picnic tables, then they started gettin high, i was like omfg, at a park..that's not right to begin with, but then at a park ugh, i wanted to beat them up lol, i hate people who do drugs.whether i know them or not.w/e.anyways lol, then it was uth, it was good.icw til the end of this month, me,cody and davis hangin..woo good times await im sure heh..and then, islands of adventure, omg, icw for jurassic park ride..what about you cody? heheheh it's gonna be a blast, not just that either..oh ya, me and lee are gonna have to run back to dueling dragons or w/e and ride with 5 mins b4 we leave again lmfao at that last year, he almost fell cause it was wet, omg that was great times that day last year..and this year will be great too..man, i so can't wait for the new Busch Gardens ride to omg lol..okay, i think i've said all i want for now lol..soo go ahead and comment, it will make you pretty dang cool, well, some of you, you could never be cool :P j/p, u have to be cool to be friends with me :P oh just kiddin again :P

 laterz dudes

*oh yes, and jessica..next week is the week :P lol


*The more life is going on, the more the Air Force is looking even better...

school today was good..played football durin tech..man, i had an awesome interception..okay, heres how it went lol...coach was qb and he was tryin to get a pass to lee for a touchdown, i reached my arm out and hit it, it bounced off lees head forward and i intercepted it, how freakin awesome is that lol :P...umm, my 3s were on today, made 5 b4 i missed 1, made lee mad so i loved it :)...other than that it was just another day, ppl bein stupid and stuff..yup, thats all for now..adios, oh ya, gots an 85 on my spanish 2 quiz go me :)..florida sucks, its to friggen hot for april!! blahh..

hehe i drove the '66 charger today, woo i loved it lol, shiftin a auto is awesome lol, fun funhehe..icw till its all mine to drive when i want :) and then the '67 woo buddy :)...except for that, this day has been boring..ima go now later

Really Cool Video.. anyways, today was a great day at school..fridays are the best..basketball was fun..john carethers was there, havnt seen him or talked to em since we won our championship..so it was nice to see em, forgot how funny he was lol..also after lunch, i hun out up stairs with cody and smithers(aka smith aka the man), good times..hehe frey hehe...in spanish 2 we were supposed have a test today, but there was a movie playin when we got to that mrs morgan was into, it ended like right as the bell rang pratically, it was nice lol.then after schoo, i went to sports authority to get some air and paintballs..also seen a pistol looking pump paintball gun for $19.95, i wanted it but i only had $11 so i couldnt lol..oh well, its prolly cheap crap anyways, but itd still be cool to have :P...thats all i gotta say for now..l8rzizal..paintballing tomorrow woo-hoo!!!

so today was an okay day at school..boring but what else is new.i played halo today, i actually won a game and finished second a bunch of other times..whats funny is i dont even own a xbox and i still do a lot better than some people lmao!!! its fun playing but socom is still better!...im like curious as to how i've sucked on 3 pointers TWO  days in a row, never has happened in consecutive days lol...anyways, still somewhat fun playin today..last nite was pretty dang funny hehehe,i gots a new favorite word heh :P ..um tomorrows uth and inside the outside is havin a concert, free woo hoo, i love that word free...but i wish some other things were also free like a phone card since im almost outta mins, cornerstone, and end of year trip to islands of adventure...well i guess thats all i gotta say for now so l8rzizal

so today i skipped school(yeah JJ thats right I skipped :P lol) and me and my dad went downtown to the Grand Prix of St.Pete practice...it was awesome...had lots of fun today...it so weird to see cars goin 100+ racing on streets u go down all the time lol..as we were leavin seen a wreck, sounded and looked soo cool lol...he hit the wall hard but walked away just fine...it was cool, could walk almost wherever u wanted to watch the practice..they were louddddd so it made it even better even tho it kinda hurt ur ear if u were like lookin left at them come down the straightaway and once they passed it hurt lol...id like to see the race on sunday but it too much $$$ so i'll settle for watchin it on espn lol..welp been a great day so far(except for sooo dang hot out walking around,like 85+ out i think)...well, thats al i gots to say for now...later people

just got done with watchin Napolean Dynamite..i liked it,good n funny n stuff..but I think its highly over rated..but thats just my opinion, id still recommend it cause its funny though...thats all adios

what a day today...it basicly ended at 12 for me cause then was lunch and then went outside from about 12:45-3:50 and played basketball the entire time...since tech and spanish 2 was also out...it was sooo freaking hot out dang...im still burning up...and my dad was late gettin me soo i played more lol...well i made a couple nice one handed over my head sots from the 3..so lucky lol...anyways, i think i proved to some people that i can play 21 without tipping...so yeah, thats not all i have to do to win...i found it more fun to play without tipping cause it shows you have more skillz lol...anyways, im about to watch napolean dynamite prolly on my pc...umm, thats it for now..dinner timeee...laterz ppl

well today, didnt do much at all...just kinda relaxed at home as my spring break is coming to a close tomorrow...been a very boring one, but its been nice to relax n stuff..so ya...today was our one monthy : )....also today i played socom 2 for a bit, my rank is gettin up there so thats cool lol...this "praetorian" from my clan sent me this thing he did with excel, its pretty sweet, has kills-death ratio etc. its awesome, im 6 outta 19 in our clan and that was as of like 2 weeks ago when he started...ive got rank up a lot n stuff..so ya lol...spring break ends tomorrow...i think im gonna get to go paintballin(for the 3rd time this spring break so it is awesome!), prolly gonna be another huge game tomorrow so thats awesome....uUmMm thats it i guess fornow..later people

went paintballing again today..wow..it was like 20+ vs 20+ each round..we didnt play the way we normally do cause there was soo many..we just played attack and defend..it was fun, the last game i played i ran outta ammo which sucked lol...but man i had a great time..cody, your a freakin loser for not bein there!!! hehe..anyways, i gotta get more paint and air b4 we play again cause i used a lot today lol...man at one point, my gun was covered in soo many different colors from splatter..i've never been hit with so much splatter ever,it was like rain of paint comin down..it was a great dayy...welp im outta here for now

went paintballin today, it wasnt a lot of fun like usual cuz just me,james,ben,cat,smithers and cody were there...cody man, ur gun is so pimp lol, i was drool drool drool lol...anyways, he was the only one who shot me lol, he sumhow lucked a head shot on me when i was right by a fort, never can happen again i guarantee lol, and the other i was runnin to go around and he started firin and nailed my leg, holy crap that hurt like a mofo..left a nice mark, thanks cody lol...well i did get around and then i was only one left and 3 of them were sittin right together, masks off guns down...i coulda shot 1 time for each and got em out, but i was nice and let em surrender basicly lol..it was hilarious with the stupid stuff goin on when we were jus hangin out after that game,smith ben and james shootin ea. other with the air and crap..me and cody were like, such childs while we were laughin our butts off..wish i had a video camera wit me...anyways, playin again tomorrow after church so i think i might go...thats it for now..im off to relax cause i was didnt get to bed til around 3 and was up at 930 about, so im tired lol...later

well, tonight i went to the Steven Curtis Chapman,Casting Crowns and Chris Tomlin concert, i guess i had a good time..the bus ride over was funny cause of Matt, we gots da best bus driver lol, hes awesome...anyways, we got there late cause of traffic and missed Casting Crowns...Chris Tomlin was really good even though he sang just a couple songs..it was amazing when he stepped away from the mic and 10,000 people just kept singing, it was awesome...well i didnt like steven cutris chapman cause he only has 2 songs i like and to be honest, i fell asleep off and on during him...icw til i can see chris tomlin again, im never gonna get tired of him : )    i was soo freaking cold tonight too lol, brrr....well ima finish my taco bell and head off to bed cause im really tired and  i gotta get up for paintballing tomorrow : )...peace

hey ppl, today at school was  a day like any other..did work, played basketball and football, u kno the norm. I was lightin up da threes today, 6 in a row before i missed one lol, i won a few games...tipped JJ : ) idk if he tip me i dont remember...paid the $27 for the Stephen Curtis Chapman, Casting Crowns and CHRIS TOMLIN!! concert today, omg omg i cant wait! its gonna be the best concert ever, not gonna be back til really late this friday, so its gonna eb awesome cause then i come home, sleep, wake up and go paintballing!! w00000t w000000t got a great weekend awaiting me, but i gotta make through a week of school first : /     man comin home from school today, i seen this sooooo sweet like old Cuda, but the thing was, it was HEMI ohh, orange omg it was nice, since i was drooling over it i kept my mouth shut this time(only a couple ppl will get that lol) but man i was jealous, but then came home, and there i see a 72 challenger, 64 chrysler new port convertible, annd now dad brought home the 67 charger...woooohoooo lol, once we bleed the brakes, ima drive that beast(i hope)   : )    welp, thats it for now i guess, btw thanks for that Pillar cd sennit...later guys

hey guys sup...today i went to the Tampa Bay Storm(arena football) game with my dad cause he got free tickets to the suites,normally cost $100..oh man, so nice, so much foood lol : )   anyways, had a great time, it was a great game, we won 59-56, gotta field goal with seconds to go w00t...on the way home, oh boy...we were cruisin along and this truck lost a mattress it was carrying, and this lil grand am ran it all way over and got sideways and was headed for the wall but holy crap was that a nice save that guy did,wow..i say like a few more inches sideways and it was goin to flip since he was goin so fast bein on interstate, it was madd crazy lol..really screwed up that dudes car, somethin was bouncin like woah underneath...anyways lol, that was pretty cool to see, wouldnt a been if he crashed cause itd been big....welp peace

hey guys..today was a good day, except for walking all the way to taco bell in the freezing rain/cold..burr lol...anyways, it rained alllllll day, so no b ball :( lol...so since everyone was done with their work after lunch(like never happens) since we couldnt go outside, we watched Aladdin, oh boyy lol...anyways, after that, had tech, did nuttin cept sit around and jus chill, after that was spanish 2 boring...then after school hung around and eventually jus said screw it and walked in the rain cause i was really hungry lol...then walked back and had uth group...idk why but tonight was like extremely good uth...i also signed the covenant thingy on the sheet, for true love waits, i felt better inside after doing that...if your readin this, you know what it is...a lot of people did it tonight which was great, if only they keep that "promise" now...id say everyone who reads this actually, prolly did it lol....I gotta get $67 so i can pay $40 registration for camp(June 12-17) w00t and the other $27 for an awesome concert featuring,Stephen Curtis Chapman, Casting Crowns and Chris Tomlin!!!!!!! its gonna be soooo great, back in sept. at rock the universe, chris tomlins concert, i say was the best concert i have ever been to..and now with him and casting crowns, this should top that..i cant wait!!!welp thats all i have to say for now...peace

well guys, its over, no more fbcs eagles b ball ever again *tear*, we went out on a winning note tho, beat ccs in tourns today 56-55, it was one heck of a game i must say..i had like 6 pts, 4 block, 2 of which i packed Paul, so it was sweet,with seconds on the clock i mentioned to coach me goin man to man on paul, and i think that made him realize we all should, and thats what won us the game cause if we wouldnt have, they woulda easily drove in and scored...well we tied with Grace for 2nd for the year, and got 3rd in tournaments..then ya'll know we got first and first in other conference last week...our final record(s)...20-4 over all i think, 17 of which were in a row...1 division we were 12-0 and of course first place, then first in tournaments..and the other 8-4 and 2nd place and then 3rd in tournaments..its a great year for us, in the all-star game, me,lee and daniel carethers were in it, us 3 scored most of our teams points, i had 10, and 3 blocks, one of which was soooooo sweet, it was so loud, we all got medals for bein all-stars..daniel c got the crap packed outta him, then the ball hit off his head and went out, i was lmao at it, along with lee, it was sooo funny, i hope i go to northside next year to stay on b ball with them two...our team lost in all stars 51-41, it was all good tho, just a game for fun...but,in the ccs game, some dude jumped on my bad ankle again, and it hurt soo bad, but i stuck it out cause i knew i had to since we only had 5 people, i had some ice on it which kept swelling down, its bruised now, and i just tried to ignore it during all-star game...welp good bye first baptist christian school eagles : (   it was the best year weve ever had and it came in the last year of the school..means a lot, btw Genesis beat Grace to win championship,
